column2: SELECT TOP # s.ra, s.dec, s.z, g.d4#_sub, gSI.v_disp, s.CLASS FROM galSpecIndx as g  JOIN SpecObj AS s  ON g.SpecobjID = s.SpecobjID JOIN galSpecLine as gSL  ON gSL.SpecobjID = s.SpecobjID JOIN galSpecInfo as gSI  ON gSI.SpecobjID = s.SpecobjID JOIN galSpecExtra as gSE  ON gSE.SpecobjID = s.SpecobjID WHERE (s.z between # and #)  AND s.CLASS = &&&
